<h2>Password Reset Request</h2>
<p>Hello {{userName}},</p>
<p>We received a request to reset your password for the Hospital Management System. If you did not make this request, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
<p>To reset your password, please click the button below:</p>
<div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
    <a href="{{resetUrl}}" class="button" style="color: white;">Reset My Password</a>
</div>
<p>This link will expire in 1 hour.</p>
<p>If you encounter any issues, please contact our IT helpdesk.</p>
